How to return an OK status?:
Use the `Return` action with `<OK: status>`.

```aro
(Confirm: Example) {
    Return an <OK: status> for the <request>.
}
```

How to iterate over a list?:
Use a `For-each` block.

```aro
(Process Items: Example) {
    For-each <item> in the <items> {
        Log <item> to the <console>.
    }
    Return an <OK: status> for the <processing>.
}
```
